oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Edward Bailey playing cards
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Double exposure photograph of Edward Bailey playing with cards in his front yard. He is seated in chairs next to a table with two bottles. Another unidentified child can be seen looking out the window of the house, on right.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Multiple exposure photographs; Children
